### Templates 模板市场接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录获取令牌
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 Anti-Forgery Token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 查询模板（支持 keyword/category/tags/version）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/templates?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&keyword=模板&category=1&tags=page,list&version=1.0
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 创建自定义模板
# @name createTemplate
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "客户详情页模板",
  "category": 1,
  "schemaJson": "{\"type\":\"page\",\"title\":\"客户详情\"}",
  "description": "客户详情展示页面模板",
  "tags": "crm,page,detail",
  "version": "1.0.1"
}

###
@templateId = {{createTemplate.response.body.$.data.id}}

### 从模板实例化
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/templates/{{templateId}}/instantiate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
